author: Home Repair Tutor
description: ZipWall dust barrier tips…I have to seal this room and contain the dust. I used four twelve foot ZipWall poles, 4 mil plastic and FoamRails. I cut the plastic to overlap adjacent walls by eight inches. That way the FoamRails can seal against the walls and baseboards. Many thanks to @zipwall_llc  for sponsoring this tutorial and making home improvement safer for everyone 🔥#dustcontrol #zipwall #homerenovation #homerepairtutor #brandpartner
